    845  f3d4							;-------------------------------------------------------------
    846  f3d4							; CheckCollision - player vs the entity on the player's floor.
    847  f3d4							;   cone  -> +1 to the BCD score, entity consumed.
    848  f3d4							;   skull -> game over (freeze + red background).
    849  f3d4							;-------------------------------------------------------------
